 h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#6757fe]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="min-w-0 flex-1 break-words text-[14px] leading-[1.4] text-[#424242]">수학동아가 대한수학회·국가수리과학연구소와 한국판 온라인 공공 수학 프로젝트를 시작했습니다.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-1"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check mt-[2px] h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#6757fe]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="min-w-0 flex-1 break-words text-[14px] leading-[1.4] text-[#424242]">이 프로젝트는 2017년 1월부터 매달 청소년 대상 도전 수학 문제를 무료로 제공하기로 했습니다.</span></li><li class="flex items-start gap-1"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check mt-[2px] h-5 w-5 shrink-0 text-[#6757fe]" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"></path></svg><span class="min-w-0 flex-1 break-words text-[14px] leading-[1.4] text-[#424242]">프린스턴대 박사과정 이석형 연구원이 업다운 게임 변형 문제를 맛보기 문제로 제시했습니다.</span></li></ul></div></div></section><div class="hidden lg:block"><div data-component="PopAiRView" class="w-full rounded-[12px] overflow-hidden shadow-[0px_6px_12px_-6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12),0px_8px_24px_-4px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)]" style="background-image:linear-gradient(132deg, rgba(205, 62, 199, 1) 4%, rgba(103, 87, 254, 1) 59%, rgba(45, 142, 250, 1) 96%)"><div class="flex justify-center pt-10 mb-4"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity flex items-center gap-[2px]" href="https://air.dongascience.com"><img alt="AiR" loading="lazy" width="112" height="28" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="h-7 w-auto" style="color:transparent" src="/dotcom/assets/logo_air.svg"/><span class="overflow-hidden text-white text-ellipsis text-[16px] font-medium leading-[140%] tracking-[-0.5px]">에 질문해보세요.</span></a></div><div class="flex flex-col gap-2 pb-2 px-10 items-start"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-start gap-[2px] hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity w-full" href="https://air.dongascience.com?q=%ED%8F%B4%EB%A6%AC%EB%A7%A4%EC%8A%A4%20%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%EC%A0%9D%ED%8A%B8%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C%EB%8A%94%20%EC%96%B4%EB%96%A4%20%EC%8B%9D%EC%9C%BC%EB%A1%9C%20%EC%88%98%ED%95%99%20%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C%EB%A5%BC%20%ED%95%A8%EA%BB%98%20%ED%92%80%EA%B9%8C%EC%9A%94%3F"><div class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 p-0.5 flex items-center justify-center"><img alt="" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-5 h-5" style="color:transparent" src="/dotcom/assets/icon_speech_bubble.svg"/></div><span class="text-white text-[14px] font-medium leading-[140%] tracking-[-0.42px] flex-1">폴리매스 프로젝트에서는 어떤 식으로 수학 문제를 함께 풀까요?</span></a></div><div class="flex justify-center pb-10 pt-4"><a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex h-[48px] max-w-[280px] w-full px-10 justify-center items-center rounded-[24px] bg-white text-[#625CFE] text-center text-[18px] font-semibold leading-[140%] tracking-[-0.54px] hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity" href="https://air.dongascience.com">과학동아AiR에게 질문하기</a></div></div></div><div class="w-full p-6 lg:p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl outline outline-1 outline-offset-[-1px] outline-black/10 flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-2 "><div class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 w-full"><div class="h-8 flex justify-start items-center gap-2"><div class="w-6 h-6 flex items-center justify-center"><img alt="Hot" loading="lazy" width="24" height="24" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="w-6 h-6" style="color:transparent" src="/dotcom/assets/icons/icon_hot.png"/></div></div><div class="flex-1 py-[3px] flex justify-start items-start"><div class="justify-start text-neutral-800 text-xl font-bold leading-relaxed">실시간 인기기사</div></div></div><div class="self-stretch flex flex-col justify-start items-start w-full mt-2"><a class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 py-4 border-b border-zinc-100" href="/ko/news/78860"><div class="py-0.5 flex justify-start items-center gap-2 w-6"><div class="w-6 text-center justify-center text-red-500 text-2xl font-black">1</div></div><div class="flex-1 inline-flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4"><div class="text-neutral-800 text-base font-medium leading-snug">위고비, 살만 빠지는 게 아니었다?!</div></div></a><a class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 py-4 border-b border-zinc-100" href="/ko/news/78856"><div class="py-0.5 flex justify-start items-center gap-2 w-6"><div class="w-6 text-center justify-center text-red-500 text-2xl font-black">2</div></div><div class="flex-1 inline-flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4"><div class="text-neutral-800 text-base font-medium leading-snug">세계적 물리학자 막스 플랑크 논문 ‘의문의 철회’ 15년 만에 취소</div></div></a><a class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 py-4 border-b border-zinc-100" href="/ko/news/78877"><div class="py-0.5 flex justify-start items-center gap-2 w-6"><div class="w-6 text-center justify-center text-red-500 text-2xl font-black">3</div></div><div class="flex-1 inline-flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4"><div class="text-neutral-800 text-base font-medium leading-snug">美 떠나 中 간 노벨상 수상자 오마르 야기…&quot;미국 연구비 삭감 등 영향&quot;</div></div></a><a class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 py-4 border-b border-zinc-100" href="/ko/news/78898"><div class="py-0.5 flex justify-start items-center gap-2 w-6"><div class="w-6 text-center justify-center text-neutral-700 text-2xl font-black">4</div></div><div class="flex-1 inline-flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4"><div class="text-neutral-800 text-base font-medium leading-snug">&#x27;전략기술 박사후연구원 산학 프로젝트&#x27; 컨소시엄 13개 선정</div></div></a><a class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 pt-4" href="/ko/news/78899"><div class="py-0.5 flex justify-start items-center gap-2 w-6"><div class="w-6 text-center justify-center text-neutral-700 text-2xl font-black">5</div></div><div class="flex-1 inline-flex flex-col justify-center items-start gap-4"><div class="text-neutral-800 text-base font-medium leading-snug">실험실에서 혈액세포가 인간 정자로…쥐 신장에서 &#x27;고환 유사 조직&#x27; 성숙</div></div></a></div></div><div class="hidden md:block"><a href="http://www.dongascience.com/redirect.php?atype=W&amp;idx=5458" target="_SELF" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block w-full hover:opacity-95 transition-opacity"><img src="https://image.dongascience.com/Photo/2026/07/17828743456455.jpg" alt="마케팅팀/기획전 고도화 페이지" class="w-full h-auto"/></a></div><div class="w-full p-6 lg:p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl outline-1 outline-offset-[-1px] outline-black/10 flex flex-col justify-start items-start gap-2 force-pt-0 force-pb-0"><div class="self-stretch inline-flex justify-start items-start gap-2 w-full"><div class="h-8 flex justify-start items-center gap-2"><div class="h-6 items-center justify-center"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-6 h-6"><path fill="#212121" d="M19 18.5a1.5 1.5 0 1 0-2.999 0 1.5 1.5 0 0 0 2.999 0M8 12a1.5 1.5 0 1 0-1.5 1.5l.148-.007A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 8 12m11-6.5A1.5 1.5 0 1 0 17.5 7l.148-.007A1.5 1.5 0 0 0 19 5.5m2 0a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-5.975 2.475l-.02-.021-5.134 3.11a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 .025 1.781l5.225 3.088a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-1.018 1.722l-5.225-3.088a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-2.205.929L6.5 15.5a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 2.308-6.13l5.26-3.187a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 .957-3.158A3.5 3.5 0 0 1 21 5.5"></path></svg></div></div><div class="flex-1 py-[3px] flex justify-start items-start"><div class="flex-1 flex items-center gap-2 text-neutral-800 text-xl font-bold leading-[140%]"><span class="break-words">SNS 공유된 기사</span></div></div></div><div class="self-stretch flex flex-col justify-start items-start w-full mt-2"><a class="self-stretch flex flex-col items-start relative" href="/ko/news/76684"><div clas